body:
A Fabric mod that lets you change the max durability of an item through an NBT tag. Very heavy inspiration from this Forge mod: [Customizable Max Durability](https://modrinth.com/mod/customizable-max-durability)

## Example 1 (A Command)
```
/give @s bow{maxDamage:1337}
```


## Example 2 (A Datapack Recipe)
```
{
  "type": "minecraft:crafting_shaped",
  "pattern": [
    " MS",
    "M S",
    " MS"
  ],
  "key": {
    "M": {
      "item": "minecraft:iron_ingot"
    },
    "S": {
      "item": "minecraft:string"
    }
  },
  "result": {
    "item": "minecraft:bow",
    "count": 1,
    "nbt": "{maxDamage:1337}"
  }
}
```
